{"tid":1155082,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"孖妹Twins十八週年 蔡氏伉儷出遊日本 擺烏龍去錯酒店","createTime":"2019-05-14T17:03:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-17T08:06:54.000Z","uid":242050,"like":6,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"e9075d507e5c462dc6d9a8904f232432d21ffc2f","tid":1155082,"uid":242050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T17:03:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tg3hPHO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTg3hPHO.png&h=c04740d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n適逢Twins 5月18日出道18週年大日子，阿Sa阿嬌繼2015年馬爾代夫行之後，再度一同兩人「度蜜月」，阿嬌丈夫更加送上酒店住宿給她們。搞笑的是，她們到達日本之後沒有立刻前往酒店，反而去共晉晚餐。晚餐後抵達酒店，酒店工作人員堅持表示沒有兩人的入住預定紀錄，阿Sa可能好似唯唯咁心諗：「我喎」。原來，二人擺烏龍去錯酒店，認真搞笑啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2240fb292c4632ec77e1019060f9b1b62fb43778","tid":1155082,"uid":32273,"like":10,"dislike":24,"score":-14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T17:12:32.000Z","msg":"左邊好老<br />\n右邊好醜"},{"pid":"eb3a239b4b8def81052a4ca15cf5a559c249e5e2","tid":1155082,"uid":242050,"like":18,"dislike":4,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"2240fb292c4632ec77e1019060f9b1b62fb43778","tid":1155082,"uid":32273,"like":10,"dislike":24,"score":-14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T17:12:32.000Z","msg":"左邊好老<br />\n右邊好醜"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T17:18:48.000Z","msg":"左邊邊到老？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b56c20aec71e635fe1bea40eaf7d20f6060f9693","tid":1155082,"uid":128210,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T18:56:15.000Z","msg":"伉儷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4547793261c31bf04546f9fb57a5b93e4b65700d","tid":1155082,"uid":15070,"like":28,"dislike":0,"